mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/2097/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, More', 'Clindamycin, Vitamin A, Fluorometholone, Dapsone, Methylprednisolone, Azelaic acid, Adapalene', 1767369485);
